<p>For the cherry on top of the release, we&#8217;ve included a tweak to the handling of really long filenames in grid fields. Why? <a href="http://scottbradlee.bandcamp.com/track/friday-vintage-swing-remake-ft-niia">Because it&#8217;s Friday</a>, and youâ€™re awesome!</p>

